{
  "$schema": "./schema/wait-baselines.schema.json",
  "_doc": [
    "Static per-attraction wait-time baselines for 12 WDW headliners.",
    "",
    "Keyed by attraction external_id (human-readable, stable). The API",
    "loader resolves these to attraction UUIDs at hydration time.",
    "",
    "Each entry has four time-of-day buckets with an average standby",
    "wait in minutes and a confidence label. Values are hand-calibrated",
    "from publicly observable ride-wait patterns (Touring Plans averages",
    "and firsthand rope-drop / evening patterns). Not gospel — good",
    "enough for v1 scoring; refine when real historical ingestion lands.",
    "",
    "Buckets:",
    "  open      park open → 11:00    (rope drop, low-to-rising)",
    "  midday    11:00 → 14:00        (peak crowds)",
    "  afternoon 14:00 → 18:00        (plateau, slight drop)",
    "  evening   18:00 → close        (tails down unless fireworks pull)",
    "",
    "Any attraction not listed here uses the solver's baseline fallback.",
    "Edit with intent — these numbers steer which rides the solver slots",
    "in the morning vs. afternoon."
  ],
  "buckets": {
